item.title: CVE-2018-14667|2024-08-05T09:38:12.990Z -- %5Bunknown%5D -- richfaces
item.description: The RichFaces Framework 3.X through 3.3.4 is vulnerable to Expression Language (EL) injection via the UserResource resource. A remote, unauthenticated attacker could exploit this to execute arbitrary code using a chain of java serialized objects via org.ajax4jsf.resource.UserResource$UriData.
